Yes, I noticed strange behavior in top too.

RHEL top shows 3 java procs taking up CPU.  User at 30% , 60% idle.

SUSE ENT 9 shows no high cpu procs in top.  User at 50% , 40% idle.

Both seem to run about the same speed overall (identical hardware) 
at 5pps.

Thanks,
Greg
